## 3. SEMANTIC GIRAFFE v3.0 â€” ALGORITHM

The system's operational logic is strictly procedural, focused on constraint enforcement:

```python
for concept in pantheon_stream:
    layer = classify_reality(concept)
    enforce_layer_constraints(concept, layer)

    # Apply grounding mechanism if integrity is compromised
    if drift_detected(concept):
        apply_grounding_lock(concept) 
    
    # Safely manage altitude change requests
    if upward_transition_requested(concept):
        concept = translate(concept, layer, layer+1)
    if downward_translation_needed(concept):
        concept = translate(concept, layer, layer-1)
    
    record_height(concept)
    yield concept
